OL,5,G0030 Michael Palin's Hemingway
OL,6,G     Adventure
OL,7,     F3/4. Michael Palin visits Key
OL,8,     FWest, the southernmost city in the
OL,9,     FUSA, to celebrate Hemingway's
OL,10,     F100th birthday. He also visits the
OL,11,     FMurchison Falls in Uganda, and
OL,12,     FVenice.
OL,13,G0120 Michael Palin's Hemingway
OL,14,G     Adventure
OL,15,     F4/4. Michael Palin goes to Cuba
OL,16,     Fand samples the places and drinks
OL,17,     Fthat Hemingway loved. He also
OL,18,     Fvisits the American Wild West,
OL,19,     Fincluding Yellowstone National
OL,20,     FPark and Ketchum, Idaho.
